Altogether, the absolute P@1 numbers still leave huge room for improvement. This shows that \convmix is indeed a challenging benchmark, with difficult user inputs where inferring the intent is hard, for example: \utterance{Which war is discussed in the book?} or \utterance{What was the final film he made?} (see Table (ref) for more examples).